des:
Do you have what it takes to be a millionaire? Test your skills with the help of this skill. And see if you are worth it or not.

-This skill work on devices with or without display.
-This skill ask you MCQ question and gives you points based on whether your answer is right or wrong.
-To start this skill say, 'Alexa, open millionaire quiz'.
